### ecommerce-microservices — sample requests (secured)
###
### All traffic now goes through the API GATEWAY on port 8080 and requires a JWT.
### Step 1: run the token request below, copy the access_token from the response.
### Step 2: paste it into the @token variable.
### Step 3: run the other requests.
###
### Start order: auth-server (9000) -> product/order/notification -> gateway (8080)

@gateway = http://localhost:8080
@authServer = http://localhost:9000
@token = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### -------------------- GET A TOKEN --------------------

### Request a client-credentials token from the auth-server
POST {{authServer}}/oauth2/token
Authorization: Basic ZWNvbW1lcmNlLWNsaWVudDplY29tbWVyY2Utc2VjcmV0
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials&scope=api.read api.write

### -------------------- PRODUCTS (via gateway) --------------------

### No token -> expect 401 Unauthorized
GET {{gateway}}/products

### With token -> expect 200 and the seeded products
GET {{gateway}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get one product
GET {{gateway}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Add a product
POST {{gateway}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop Stand",
  "description": "Aluminium adjustable stand",
  "price": 34.50,
  "availableStock": 40
}

### Update a product
PUT {{gateway}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Wireless Mouse (v2)",
  "description": "Updated ergonomic mouse",
  "price": 27.99,
  "availableStock": 120
}

### -------------------- ORDERS (via gateway) --------------------

### Place an order. order-service reserves stock from product-service (with its own
### service token) and fires a notification.
POST {{gateway}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Ada Lovelace",
  "customerEmail": "ada@example.com",
  "items": [
    { "productId": 1, "quantity": 2 },
    { "productId": 2, "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

### Order exceeding stock -> 422
POST {{gateway}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Greedy Buyer",
  "customerEmail": "greedy@example.com",
  "items": [
    { "productId": 4, "quantity": 99999 }
  ]
}

### List all orders
GET {{gateway}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get one order
GET {{gateway}}/orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### -------------------- NOTIFICATIONS (via gateway) --------------------

### List notifications
GET {{gateway}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Send one directly
POST {{gateway}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipient": "ada@example.com",
  "channel": "EMAIL",
  "subject": "Test",
  "message": "Hello from the notification service",
  "relatedOrderId": null
}
